I can reproduce it only if I disable `AdGuard Popups filter`.

You can try to add following rules to user rules:
```adblock
indiatimes.com#$#body { overflow: auto !important; }
indiatimes.com#$#.popupbgLayer { display: none !important; }
indiatimes.com#$#.adblocker_popup { display: none !important; }
```

